1
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:26,378
[Kyosuke Higuchi] Then, once you're
fully convinced that I'm the real thing,

2
00:01:26,503 --> 00:01:28,380
-you and I can get married.
-[gasping]

3
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:30,382
And so, based on what he said,

4
00:01:30,757 --> 00:01:32,134
Higuchi is Kira.

5
00:01:32,426 --> 00:01:35,345
GUIDANCE

6
00:01:36,972 --> 00:01:39,641
[tense music playing]

7
00:01:46,690 --> 00:01:48,817
[L] If the killing of criminals stops now,

8
00:01:48,984 --> 00:01:52,237
then there's no doubt that Higuchi
is the one with Kira's powers.

9
00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:54,531
However...

10
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,826
I knew that Amane would do
almost anything for Light Yagami, but…

11
00:01:58,118 --> 00:02:00,412
but to think she would
actually go this far?

12
00:02:00,912 --> 00:02:04,499
If criminals do stop dying after this
it will make it difficult to determine

13
00:02:04,750 --> 00:02:08,295
a critical element:
How Kira conducts his murders.

14
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:11,214
I have to think of a plan.

15
00:02:12,049 --> 00:02:15,260
Misa, how did you get Higuchi to confess?

16
00:02:15,552 --> 00:02:18,096
Easy. That guy is totally in love with me.

17
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:21,266
All I had to do was tell him
I'd marry him if he was really Kira.

18
00:02:21,433 --> 00:02:24,728
Plus, I managed to convince him
that I'm the second Kira.

19
00:02:25,187 --> 00:02:26,730
[Misa Amane] If I didn't say this now,

20
00:02:26,855 --> 00:02:29,316
I'd probably end up
contradicting my story later.

21
00:02:29,983 --> 00:02:33,362
Misa, you idiot!
Didn't I tell you to deny all that?

22
00:02:33,862 --> 00:02:36,448
[Misa]
But now we know Higuchi is Kira, right?

23
00:02:36,573 --> 00:02:38,950
So what's the problem?
Can't we just catch him?

24
00:02:39,618 --> 00:02:42,871
I suppose this is what you would call
a victory, right? Matsuda?

25
00:02:43,205 --> 00:02:44,331
[Light chuckles]

26
00:02:44,414 --> 00:02:47,959
But right now, we still don't know exactly
how he kills his victims, do we.

27
00:02:48,251 --> 00:02:49,961
Yes, that's what I was thinking.

28
00:02:50,379 --> 00:02:52,381
Before we move to arrest Higuchi,

29
00:02:52,714 --> 00:02:55,258
I want to find out how he kills people.

30
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:58,095
If the criminals stop dying,
we'll be able to figure it out,

31
00:02:58,178 --> 00:02:59,888
unless we come up with another idea.

32
00:02:59,971 --> 00:03:01,014
Isn't that right?

33
00:03:01,473 --> 00:03:04,434
Yes. At any rate,
even if we do arrest Higuchi,

34
00:03:04,518 --> 00:03:05,644
we're not going to do it

35
00:03:05,727 --> 00:03:08,522
until we're certain
that criminals have stopped dying.

36
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:10,607
Let me think about this for a moment.

37
00:03:12,943 --> 00:03:14,736
-[L] Wedy.
-[Wedy] Yeah.

38
00:03:14,945 --> 00:03:16,822
An update on the current situation,
please.

39
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,740
[Wedy]
Everything's going smoothly.

40
00:03:18,824 --> 00:03:21,243
We should be able to track 70%
of their movements

41
00:03:21,368 --> 00:03:23,787
using our cameras
inside the office building.

42
00:03:24,204 --> 00:03:25,664
[L]
What about outside of the office?

43
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,625
That's not going to be possible
with just Watari and me.

44
00:03:29,376 --> 00:03:31,336
What if you just focus solely on Higuchi?

45
00:03:31,712 --> 00:03:32,629
Higuchi?

46
00:03:33,213 --> 00:03:36,842
I've only been able to enter the houses
of five of the men, so far.

47
00:03:37,175 --> 00:03:41,054
But Mido, Namikawa and Higuchi's
all have super high tech security systems.

48
00:03:41,304 --> 00:03:42,389
Especially Higuchi.

49
00:03:43,014 --> 00:03:46,560
He recently constructed a dampening room
that shuts out any electronic waves.

50
00:03:46,727 --> 00:03:48,812
It took me two days
just to break into the place.

51
00:03:49,271 --> 00:03:51,189
This guy sure does sound suspicious.

52
00:03:51,314 --> 00:03:55,986
Hmm. All right. Then begin installing
microphones, trackers, and cameras.

53
00:03:56,528 --> 00:03:59,740
But not in the house.
Instead just put them in every car.

54
00:04:00,031 --> 00:04:01,783
[Wedy] What? After getting this far?

55
00:04:02,659 --> 00:04:05,579
Do you know how difficult it is
to get break into someone's house?

56
00:04:05,662 --> 00:04:08,165
Besides, do you have any idea
how many cars this guy has?

57
00:04:08,331 --> 00:04:09,708
[L] He has six.

58
00:04:10,459 --> 00:04:13,754
Fine then. I just have to install them
in all his cars, right?

59
00:04:15,213 --> 00:04:16,423
Yes, thank you.

60
00:04:18,049 --> 00:04:22,304
[Misa] Oh, if Higuchi had been bugged
earlier, I would have been in big trouble.

61
00:04:27,434 --> 00:04:31,396
[L] Light, I'm sorry
to keep coming back to this topic...

62
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,565
I'll just get right to the point...

63
00:04:33,815 --> 00:04:34,775
[Light] What is it?

64
00:04:35,525 --> 00:04:38,653
Do you remember?
Killing anyone, I mean?

65
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:39,946
[Light] Huh?

66
00:04:41,156 --> 00:04:43,241
[upset] Are you still going on about that?

67
00:04:43,366 --> 00:04:45,368
Look, I'm not Kira. How many times do I--

68
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:47,454
I just want you to answer the question.

69
00:04:48,538 --> 00:04:50,415
Well, do you remember?

70
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:53,043
No, I don't.

71
00:04:53,418 --> 00:04:54,586
Misa, what about you?

72
00:04:54,836 --> 00:04:57,964
I don't remember.
How could I, because I'm not Kira.

73
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:02,511
Look, Light. Please listen to
what I'm about to say.

74
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:06,515
I'd like you to thoroughly analyze
my current theory.

75
00:05:07,307 --> 00:05:10,560
This could determine the way
in which we end up catching Kira.

76
00:05:13,396 --> 00:05:15,690
[L] Light Yagami used to be Kira.

77
00:05:16,066 --> 00:05:18,735
Kira's power has somehow
passed on to another person.

78
00:05:19,152 --> 00:05:22,948
Light Yagami now has no memory
of ever being Kira.

79
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,659
I need your analysis,
based on these assumptions.

80
00:05:26,117 --> 00:05:27,828
Do you think you can do that for me?

81
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,789
[Light] Yeah, I'll give it a try.

82
00:05:32,958 --> 00:05:34,876
[L] Light Yagami used to be Kira.

83
00:05:35,168 --> 00:05:38,171
Kira's power has somehow been passed on
to another person.

84
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:40,715
Was that because Light Yagami
wanted that to happen?

85
00:05:40,966 --> 00:05:43,260
Or was there someone else
in control of Light,

86
00:05:43,426 --> 00:05:46,137
lurking in the background,
who gave him the power?

87
00:05:46,304 --> 00:05:49,558
Was it that person who passed
Light's powers to someone else?

88
00:06:03,697 --> 00:06:06,408
Given your premise,
it would be my will.

89
00:06:10,662 --> 00:06:11,872
[L] Yes, of course.

90
00:06:12,372 --> 00:06:16,710
If there is a third party with the ability
to bestow or transfer Kira's power,

91
00:06:16,918 --> 00:06:18,879
and they didn't want their method
to be discovered,

92
00:06:19,045 --> 00:06:20,922
It makes no sense
that they would wait so long

93
00:06:21,006 --> 00:06:23,049
to transfer it from you to the next Kira.

94
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:27,596
If we believe that this was the work
of some being, watching us from above,

95
00:06:27,762 --> 00:06:30,432
then we'd have to accept
that they are impossible to catch.

96
00:06:30,765 --> 00:06:33,310
Not to mention that I'd already be dead,

97
00:06:33,393 --> 00:06:35,937
or at the very least I'm being made
to be a fool

98
00:06:36,021 --> 00:06:39,024
by eternally dancing in the palm
of someone's hand.

99
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:42,360
It's highly unlikely
that such a being exists.

100
00:06:44,988 --> 00:06:47,574
[L] Even if Light Yagami was Kira…

101
00:06:49,826 --> 00:06:53,496
Kira's power can only be transferred by
the will of the person who possesses it.

102
00:06:54,581 --> 00:06:58,668
Thank you, Light. I can now say
that I feel 99 percent better.

103
00:07:09,179 --> 00:07:11,181
We'll create a situation where Higuchi

104
00:07:11,264 --> 00:07:13,350
will not be able
to pass on his power to anyone else

105
00:07:14,059 --> 00:07:15,769
We'll have him show us
how he kills.

106
00:07:16,436 --> 00:07:17,771
So, what are you going to do?

107
00:07:17,979 --> 00:07:20,440
[L] I'm going to trick Higuchi
using Sakura TV.

108
00:07:20,649 --> 00:07:22,651
-Like a hidden camera show!
-[Misa] What?

109
00:07:23,193 --> 00:07:26,404
[L] We'll use The Kira Special
that Demegawa airs every week.

110
00:07:26,821 --> 00:07:30,742
We'll book a three hour time slot.
It'll be announced that Kira's identity

111
00:07:30,867 --> 00:07:33,203
will be revealed
near the end of the special.

112
00:07:33,703 --> 00:07:35,538
Would anyone actually buy that, though?

113
00:07:35,664 --> 00:07:37,499
This is Sakura TV, after all.

114
00:07:37,874 --> 00:07:40,585
[Matsuda] For all we know,
Higuchi might not even watch that program.

115
00:07:41,628 --> 00:07:43,505
We'll get Namikawa to call him
and say

116
00:07:43,838 --> 00:07:48,218
"This is bad. Turn on your TV."
That should be enough to get him watching.

117
00:07:48,885 --> 00:07:52,180
[Light] Higuchi will buy it once he
realizes that the special guest on TV

118
00:07:52,347 --> 00:07:54,182
is someone who knows his secret.

119
00:07:54,766 --> 00:07:56,935
Oh, I get it.
So, we'll be using Aiber, then.

120
00:07:57,727 --> 00:08:00,146
[Matsuda]
He'll reveal that he was a spy all along.

121
00:08:00,563 --> 00:08:02,315
No, I'm afraid you're incorrect.

122
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,275
We will not be using Aiber.

123
00:08:06,361 --> 00:08:08,363
[L] Whoever appears on the show...

124
00:08:09,698 --> 00:08:12,993
has to be someone who Higuchi believes
he'll be able to kill.

125
00:08:13,576 --> 00:08:18,373
[L] In other words, it has to be someone
whose name he can look up easily.

126
00:08:18,832 --> 00:08:21,209
But we're never going to find
a person like that, are we?

127
00:08:21,418 --> 00:08:22,502
[everyone] Hmm...

128
00:08:23,128 --> 00:08:25,505
-You're the only one who can do it.
-Matsu!

129
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,007
Matsuda.

130
00:08:27,132 --> 00:08:29,676
Higuchi probably thinks that
you were listening in on their meeting.

131
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:31,302
and overheard their plans
to kill people.

132
00:08:31,928 --> 00:08:34,472
[Light] It would make sense that
Misa's manager, who he thought was dead,

133
00:08:34,556 --> 00:08:36,933
-is the one revealing his secret.
-That's right.

134
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:40,311
We'll have Sakura TV use a voice filter
and frosted glass

135
00:08:40,478 --> 00:08:41,479
to protect your identity.

136
00:08:42,355 --> 00:08:45,442
Higuchi will probably realize from
the announcement and the silhouette

137
00:08:45,525 --> 00:08:47,110
that it's the manager, Taro Matsui.

138
00:08:47,318 --> 00:08:49,946
[L] And just to make sure,
we'll have the studio mess up

139
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:53,199
and accidentally reveal your face
from behind the frosted glass.

140
00:08:53,324 --> 00:08:55,243
Wow! Sounds exciting.

141
00:08:55,618 --> 00:08:58,455
[L] Until the show ends, the announcer
will keep saying they'll reveal

142
00:08:58,621 --> 00:09:00,415
the full name of H,
who's acting as Kira.

143
00:09:00,915 --> 00:09:02,292
Higuchi would feel cornered.

144
00:09:02,417 --> 00:09:05,628
He'd have no choice but to find out
the manager's name as soon as possible.

145
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:08,506
We can anticipate what actions he'll take.

146
00:09:08,882 --> 00:09:10,633
We'll witness his killing method.

147
00:09:11,217 --> 00:09:13,219
After that, we arrest him.

148
00:09:14,888 --> 00:09:17,682
There is one potential problem
with this plan.

149
00:09:18,391 --> 00:09:20,685
If Higuchi can kill
by simply looking at someone's face,

150
00:09:21,227 --> 00:09:22,729
just like the second Kira...

151
00:09:24,314 --> 00:09:26,441
-Matsuda will die.
-[gasps]

152
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:30,070
But, considering the fact
that you're still alive,

153
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:32,864
and how he's pursuing Misa,
I doubt that's the case.

154
00:09:33,031 --> 00:09:34,908
[L] At any rate,
we're only going to do this

155
00:09:34,991 --> 00:09:36,367
once criminals stop dying.

156
00:09:36,493 --> 00:09:39,245
We'll have to wait for two or three days
to see whether or not that happens.

157
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,664
[L] In the meantime,
Matsuda will have to decide

158
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:43,583
if he wants to go through
with this plan.

159
00:09:46,044 --> 00:09:47,003
Hm.

160
00:09:51,424 --> 00:09:53,510
[Matsuda] I don't need two or three days
to decide.

161
00:09:54,886 --> 00:09:56,387
I want to do this.

162
00:10:24,249 --> 00:10:26,751
[Reiji Namikawa] Well I'm here.
What's with this private meeting?

163
00:10:27,377 --> 00:10:30,046
Namikawa, tell me,
who do you think is Kira?

164
00:10:30,922 --> 00:10:33,299
[scoffs]
Why do you want to know what I think?

165
00:10:33,716 --> 00:10:36,970
Besides, for all I know,
it could be you, Shimura.

166
00:10:37,137 --> 00:10:38,638
Or maybe even Mido.

167
00:10:39,097 --> 00:10:40,723
Shimura can't be Kira,

168
00:10:40,932 --> 00:10:42,642
he was the one who came crying to me

169
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:45,103
about how he can't go along
with Kira's crimes anymore.

170
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:48,982
Really? But if Mido had turned out
to be Kira, you would have been killed.

171
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:53,111
No, you and Mido would have
been successful on your own.

172
00:10:53,486 --> 00:10:56,739
There's no way either of you would need
to hold those stupid meetings,

173
00:10:57,157 --> 00:10:58,491
let alone with seven others.

174
00:10:58,616 --> 00:11:01,619
[Shimura] I can at least see that much.
We're all cooperating with these killings

175
00:11:01,703 --> 00:11:03,496
because we're afraid
of Kira turning on us.

176
00:11:03,997 --> 00:11:07,750
I mean it's only a matter of time
until the public finds out.

177
00:11:08,376 --> 00:11:11,171
And this isn't going to stop
until that happens.

178
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:16,050
So, Shimura, let me ask you then.
Who do you think Kira might be?

179
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,928
Takahashi or Higuchi.

180
00:11:19,345 --> 00:11:21,472
No, Takahashi is just a decoy.

181
00:11:22,515 --> 00:11:25,101
Kira would make sure
there are people less clever than him.

182
00:11:25,435 --> 00:11:28,479
Huh. Well then it looks like
we all know the truth already.

183
00:11:29,772 --> 00:11:31,524
[Namikawa] It's Higuchi, isn't it.

184
00:11:31,608 --> 00:11:35,361
Yes, he's the one who's most obsessed
with money and success.

185
00:11:36,070 --> 00:11:38,907
He might always act like
he's not interested in those things,

186
00:11:39,115 --> 00:11:41,117
but that just proves it all the more.

187
00:11:41,409 --> 00:11:45,288
And he always insults everyone around him
and can't use his people well.

188
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:47,373
I believe that's why he was demoted

189
00:11:47,457 --> 00:11:49,500
from being head of
the development department.

190
00:11:49,959 --> 00:11:52,962
By the way, I meant to ask,
was I the only one you invited here?

191
00:11:53,129 --> 00:11:55,048
[Shingo Mido] I also invited Ooi, but...

192
00:11:55,423 --> 00:11:58,593
but he said, "You can hold your stupid,
private meetings by yourself."

193
00:11:58,843 --> 00:12:00,345
-Go figure.
-[Namikawa] Ha!

194
00:12:00,511 --> 00:12:02,430
Good old Ooi,
always the blunt one.

195
00:12:02,722 --> 00:12:05,475
[Mido] We can also rule out Kida
as a possible suspect,

196
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:08,061
as he was the one who provided
the account for funds

197
00:12:08,186 --> 00:12:09,646
in order to commission Coil.

198
00:12:09,854 --> 00:12:13,107
Namikawa, during that first meeting
after Hatori died,

199
00:12:13,483 --> 00:12:15,068
you got a call on your cell phone.

200
00:12:15,235 --> 00:12:16,945
I was wondering who it was from.

201
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:20,198
Hm, you know, Shimura,
you're really are a sharp one.

202
00:12:20,615 --> 00:12:24,202
Kira probably selected you
because he appreciates your caution.

203
00:12:24,452 --> 00:12:26,371
[phone rings]

204
00:12:27,956 --> 00:12:29,207
[Namikawa] Hm.

205
00:12:31,459 --> 00:12:32,335
Namikawa speaking.

206
00:12:32,627 --> 00:12:33,753
It's L.

207
00:12:34,003 --> 00:12:37,215
-Before I go on, are you by yourself?
-No.

208
00:12:37,382 --> 00:12:39,300
[Light] Then just act like
it's a normal call again.

209
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,177
I don't think there's any need for that.

210
00:12:41,261 --> 00:12:44,305
One of the people here with me
was just expressing his suspicions

211
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,807
about your last phone call.

212
00:12:46,057 --> 00:12:47,850
Who is that on the line? Namikawa?

213
00:12:48,935 --> 00:12:51,396
-It's L.
-[gasping]

214
00:12:53,106 --> 00:12:55,650
L, Mido and Shimura are here as well.

215
00:12:56,276 --> 00:12:58,486
I'm reasonably certain
that neither of them are Kira.

216
00:12:58,611 --> 00:13:00,905
In fact, they seem fed up with it
at this point.

217
00:13:00,989 --> 00:13:03,074
I'll speak for them and say
they choose to stand back

218
00:13:03,157 --> 00:13:05,868
and watch your face-off with Kira,
like I plan to.

219
00:13:05,952 --> 00:13:07,412
Hm. That's fine.

220
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:10,164
Tonight, I'm going to catch Kira.

221
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,292
But I'll need a favor from you.

222
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:13,751
[Namikawa] Hm.

223
00:13:15,169 --> 00:13:16,629
Then it's the end for Higuchi.

224
00:13:17,046 --> 00:13:18,256
What? You know that it's him?

225
00:13:18,965 --> 00:13:21,968
Ha! So even the great L
can be tricked.

226
00:13:22,385 --> 00:13:23,428
Based on your reaction,

227
00:13:23,553 --> 00:13:26,306
I'm now a hundred percent certain
that Higuchi is Kira.

228
00:13:27,473 --> 00:13:29,392
Namikawa is pretty smart, huh?

229
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:31,894
But then I always thought he was,
from looking at his face.

230
00:13:32,061 --> 00:13:33,062
I guess this proves it.

231
00:13:33,313 --> 00:13:35,648
No, that was just because Light messed up.

232
00:13:36,858 --> 00:13:39,861
I'm baiting Higuchi
with a staged TV special tonight,

233
00:13:40,194 --> 00:13:41,571
Sakura TV.

234
00:13:41,988 --> 00:13:45,199
[Light] A few minutes into the program,
I want you to contact Higuchi.

235
00:13:45,325 --> 00:13:47,660
Tell him to tune in.
Do that for me

236
00:13:47,827 --> 00:13:50,330
and I won't go after you
or any of the other five.

237
00:13:50,705 --> 00:13:52,749
If the others, Kida, Takahashi,

238
00:13:52,874 --> 00:13:54,751
and Ooi if they try to do anything,

239
00:13:55,001 --> 00:13:56,336
make sure to stop them.

240
00:13:56,544 --> 00:13:57,754
All right, I understand.

241
00:14:01,341 --> 00:14:03,217
It seems it really was Higuchi.

242
00:14:04,093 --> 00:14:06,137
He'll be captured tonight, apparently.

243
00:14:07,138 --> 00:14:09,307
[laughing]

244
00:14:09,849 --> 00:14:12,852
It's been about three days
since I stopped killing criminals.

245
00:14:13,019 --> 00:14:14,771
That should be good enough,
shouldn't it?

246
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:19,442
Now, when I marry Misa Amane,
The Second Kira...

247
00:14:20,234 --> 00:14:22,195
I'll have the Shinigami eyes.

248
00:14:22,445 --> 00:14:26,616
With that power in my hands,
Yotsuba will be under my control.

249
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:29,077
[laughs maniacally]

250
00:14:29,911 --> 00:14:31,662
[phone rings]

251
00:14:34,749 --> 00:14:36,167
Higuchi, we've got a problem.

252
00:14:36,334 --> 00:14:38,628
Turn on the television.
Check out Sakura TV.

253
00:14:39,337 --> 00:14:40,296
[Higuchi] Hm?

254
00:14:41,047 --> 00:14:41,964
KIRA'S IDENTITY

255
00:14:42,048 --> 00:14:44,092
[MC] So, you're saying
one of those people is Kira, right?

256
00:14:44,175 --> 00:14:46,969
[Matsuda, voice disguised] Yes. I've got
a lot of evidence to prove it, too.

257
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,596
What the hell is this?

258
00:14:48,763 --> 00:14:51,474
Come on, it's probably a hoax.
This is Sakura TV.

259
00:14:51,641 --> 00:14:53,059
[Namikawa] No, it's more than that.

260
00:14:53,142 --> 00:14:55,019
At the beginning of the show
he said he overheard

261
00:14:55,144 --> 00:14:57,063
a meeting,
between eight people.

262
00:14:58,106 --> 00:15:00,316
[Higuchi] What?
Someone who knows about the meetings?

263
00:15:00,525 --> 00:15:02,735
Who is it? Did someone betray us?

264
00:15:03,027 --> 00:15:06,447
[Matsuda] One of them was killed by Kira
and now there are only seven left.

265
00:15:06,572 --> 00:15:08,574
The man who died was Mr. H.

266
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:10,743
[Higuchi]
Mr. H? Hatori…

267
00:15:11,369 --> 00:15:13,913
If he knows this much,
he could be one of the other six.

268
00:15:14,414 --> 00:15:15,790
No, maybe it's Coil?

269
00:15:16,082 --> 00:15:17,917
[Matsuda] Mr. H wanted to leave
the meetings

270
00:15:18,042 --> 00:15:20,086
and was killed by Kira because of that.

271
00:15:20,545 --> 00:15:22,296
[Higuchi] No, it can't be any
of the others,

272
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:24,424
there's no benefit for them
to do this.

273
00:15:24,674 --> 00:15:26,926
But no one else knows about the meetings,
do they?

274
00:15:27,176 --> 00:15:28,678
Damn it, who is it?
What?

275
00:15:29,095 --> 00:15:30,847
Wait, could it be...

276
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:33,057
-[scraping sound]
-[Matsuda winces]

277
00:15:35,476 --> 00:15:36,978
It's-- it’s him!

278
00:15:37,228 --> 00:15:39,730
[clamoring]

279
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:43,234
It's Misa's manager.
Matsui, that's his name.

280
00:15:43,401 --> 00:15:44,527
Why is he still alive?

281
00:15:47,738 --> 00:15:50,575
[Namikawa] He explained earlier
that he thought he was going to be killed.

282
00:15:50,658 --> 00:15:52,577
He pretended to fall out of
the apartment window

283
00:15:52,743 --> 00:15:55,204
and escaped to a balcony
a few floors below.

284
00:15:56,706 --> 00:15:59,292
[Higuchi] That can't be.
Just to be careful, I went home that night

285
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:02,420
and wrote his name in the notebook
like it was written on his business card.

286
00:16:02,503 --> 00:16:03,379
TARO MATSUI

287
00:16:03,463 --> 00:16:04,630
[Higuchi] Why is he still alive then?

288
00:16:04,881 --> 00:16:06,924
Could he be a former entertainer
who became a manager

289
00:16:07,008 --> 00:16:08,426
using his stage name?

290
00:16:08,885 --> 00:16:10,219
Is that possible?

291
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:11,554
If that weren't bad enough,

292
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:14,474
he said that he continued
to investigate Yotsuba up until now

293
00:16:14,557 --> 00:16:16,726
and he's figured out
which one of us is Kira.

294
00:16:17,143 --> 00:16:19,312
I'm contacting everyone right now
to let them know.

295
00:16:19,979 --> 00:16:21,981
All right. We'll talk later.

296
00:16:23,691 --> 00:16:26,569
[MC] Sir, we are terribly sorry
for that accident. Are you all right?

297
00:16:27,028 --> 00:16:28,237
We can stop if you want.

298
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:31,616
[Matsuda] No. I knew I was going to be
in danger going into this.

299
00:16:31,866 --> 00:16:33,451
This is for the sake of justice.

300
00:16:33,618 --> 00:16:36,245
So I'll see it through to the end
even if it means my death.

301
00:16:36,329 --> 00:16:38,039
[man] Yeah, that's perfect.

302
00:16:38,331 --> 00:16:40,124
Listen, just be sure to hold off on

303
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:42,793
the Kira announcement
until the last minute, all right?

304
00:16:44,128 --> 00:16:45,338
[Higuchi]
I have to kill him.

305
00:16:46,214 --> 00:16:48,591
Calm down. Misa knows his face,

306
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:51,219
so if she's the Second Kira,
she should know what his real name is.

307
00:16:51,552 --> 00:16:52,595
[phone beeps]

308
00:16:53,638 --> 00:16:55,556
[phone rings]

309
00:16:57,058 --> 00:16:58,226
It's him.

310
00:16:58,893 --> 00:17:00,228
-[busy signal]
-[Higuchi groans]

311
00:17:00,561 --> 00:17:01,854
What the hell.

312
00:17:02,021 --> 00:17:03,648
[Matsuda] To be honest,
I've been debating

313
00:17:03,731 --> 00:17:06,150
for a long time whether or not
I should make this announcement.

314
00:17:06,234 --> 00:17:09,529
But now that I'm here, I know I've done
the right thing in coming forward.

315
00:17:10,112 --> 00:17:11,322
This is bad.

316
00:17:11,489 --> 00:17:13,157
Who knows
when they'll make the announcement

317
00:17:13,241 --> 00:17:15,034
[MC] ...Kira's identity will be
announced soon.

318
00:17:15,785 --> 00:17:16,661
[phone rings]

319
00:17:16,786 --> 00:17:18,079
[voice-over on TV]
Cosme Misa.

320
00:17:18,287 --> 00:17:21,374
-A devilish charm, an angel's glitter…
-[Misa giggles on-screen]

321
00:17:21,666 --> 00:17:24,794
Misa's new line of lipstick.
Just for you.

322
00:17:25,711 --> 00:17:26,837
Mido, it's me.

323
00:17:26,963 --> 00:17:28,464
Are you watching Sakura TV?

324
00:17:28,589 --> 00:17:30,925
Why don't you call your father
at the House of Councilors.

325
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:33,928
Have him pulls some strings
at the Ministry of Internal Affairs

326
00:17:34,011 --> 00:17:34,971
to stop this broadcast.

327
00:17:35,096 --> 00:17:37,139
I'm watching but I don't think
we could stop it.

328
00:17:37,557 --> 00:17:38,891
[Mido] No one believes this program

329
00:17:39,058 --> 00:17:41,561
so we'd only make ourselves
look suspicious if we stop it.

330
00:17:41,644 --> 00:17:42,562
[gasps]

331
00:17:42,645 --> 00:17:44,647
Besides, there shouldn't be
anything to worry about.

332
00:17:45,106 --> 00:17:46,899
That guy revealed his face earlier.

333
00:17:47,275 --> 00:17:49,402
Everyone knows it's really Taro Matsui.

334
00:17:50,778 --> 00:17:53,864
Namikawa has already gone ahead
and told to watch the show.

335
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:56,325
Since one of us seven has to be Kira,

336
00:17:56,492 --> 00:17:58,369
that should mean
Taro Matsui will soon be dead.

337
00:17:58,786 --> 00:18:00,580
-Right?
-[Higuchi] Of course.

338
00:18:00,705 --> 00:18:03,165
I'm the only one who knows
or even suspects

339
00:18:03,249 --> 00:18:05,626
that Taro Matsui
isn't his real name.

340
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:10,131
That means, if I say anything,
it will reveal the fact that I'm Kira.

341
00:18:12,091 --> 00:18:13,342
-[MC] That's right...
-Yeah,

342
00:18:13,467 --> 00:18:15,720
that's true. I'll talk to you later.

343
00:18:15,928 --> 00:18:17,680
[MC] Stay tuned to Sakura TV

344
00:18:18,014 --> 00:18:19,181
Damn it!
[dials number]

345
00:18:19,307 --> 00:18:20,308
[computer beeps]

346
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:24,145
[Soichiro Yagami] Ryuzaki, Mogi is in
position in front of Yoshida Productions.

347
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:26,105
He's just received a call from Higuchi.

348
00:18:26,397 --> 00:18:29,400
Yes, it's time for phase two.
Everything's as planned.

349
00:18:29,775 --> 00:18:31,110
[Higuchi] Moji, where's Misa?

350
00:18:31,652 --> 00:18:34,196
[Mogi] Oh, Mr. Higuchi,
a pleasure to hear from you.

351
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:37,241
I'm sorry but Misa Misa is taking
a much-needed vacation right now.

352
00:18:37,408 --> 00:18:39,744
She should be back by, oh,
tomorrow morning though.

353
00:18:39,869 --> 00:18:40,828
You can reach her then.

354
00:18:40,911 --> 00:18:42,997
[Higuchi] I'm asking you
where she is now.

355
00:18:43,122 --> 00:18:44,707
[Mogi] Well that's private information.

356
00:18:44,915 --> 00:18:46,917
She's requested
that no one know where she is.

357
00:18:47,043 --> 00:18:50,212
I'm very sorry. I'll have her contact you
tomorrow, first thing.

358
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,298
[Higuchi] Damn. I know his face.

359
00:18:52,465 --> 00:18:55,676
I could kill him at any time,
if I only knew his name!

360
00:18:56,761 --> 00:18:59,680
Do you know if Misa's former manager was
an entertainer at some point?

361
00:18:59,805 --> 00:19:02,850
-Come again?
-[Higuchi] I'm talking about Taro Matsui.

362
00:19:02,975 --> 00:19:06,729
[Mogi] Oh. I was only recently hired
[chuckles] so I don't know much about him.

363
00:19:06,896 --> 00:19:09,732
If you need some information I can let you
talk to someone from the office

364
00:19:09,857 --> 00:19:12,818
I just remembered, everyone's in Okinawa
at the moment.

365
00:19:12,943 --> 00:19:14,612
You could try calling the president,
though.

366
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:17,823
This is going exactly as I planned.
It's almost scary.

367
00:19:18,157 --> 00:19:20,743
You shouldn't be scared, Light.
You should be happy.

368
00:19:20,951 --> 00:19:22,787
[Yagami]
I'm patching you into Higuchi's call

369
00:19:22,870 --> 00:19:24,955
with the president of Yoshida Productions

370
00:19:25,081 --> 00:19:26,666
[Higuchi] This is Higuchi from Yotsuba.

371
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:28,918
That manager's real name
isn't Taro Matsui...

372
00:19:29,251 --> 00:19:32,380
He's not even pretending to hide
what he's asking about now, is he.

373
00:19:32,505 --> 00:19:33,464
Stupid Higuchi.

374
00:19:33,589 --> 00:19:36,384
If he's acting like that
it's proof he's beginning to panic.

375
00:19:36,634 --> 00:19:38,135
Then what was his real name?

376
00:19:38,219 --> 00:19:41,722
[President of YP] I think it was Yamada…
No, wait... Yamashita.

377
00:19:41,972 --> 00:19:45,101
Yeah. And his first name was…
I'm sorry, I can't remember.

378
00:19:45,267 --> 00:19:46,519
[yelling] Don't screw with me!

379
00:19:46,644 --> 00:19:49,897
Why the hell can't you remember
the names of the people you hire?

380
00:19:50,398 --> 00:19:52,775
[President of YP] All right, no need
for that kind of language.

381
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:55,277
I've got his personnel file
back at the office.

382
00:19:55,361 --> 00:19:57,279
Then go back there and get it.

383
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,990
[President of YP] You've gotta be
kidding me. Give me a break.

384
00:20:00,324 --> 00:20:02,910
We're on our first company vacation
in two years!

385
00:20:03,411 --> 00:20:04,995
But if you want to know that badly,

386
00:20:05,121 --> 00:20:06,997
I'll give you the pin code
for the office lock.

387
00:20:07,123 --> 00:20:09,291
You can go in yourself
and look it up, how's that?

388
00:20:10,209 --> 00:20:12,920
The personnel files are in the desk
at the back to the left.

389
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:14,714
You'll find them filed in
the bottom drawer.

390
00:20:14,922 --> 00:20:16,924
They should all be sorted alphabetically.

391
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:19,719
But I'm pretty sure it was Yamashita.

392
00:20:19,969 --> 00:20:22,471
[Higuchi] If they're going to announce
at the end of the program,

393
00:20:22,888 --> 00:20:24,348
that means I have two hours.

394
00:20:28,686 --> 00:20:30,146
[Misa] So, what's he going to do?

395
00:20:36,861 --> 00:20:38,112
[engine revs]

396
00:20:50,124 --> 00:20:51,292
[Wedy] I see Higuchi.

397
00:20:51,375 --> 00:20:54,336
He's only carrying a single bag.
I'm in pursuit.

398
00:20:57,047 --> 00:20:58,966
Everything is still going
according to plan.

399
00:20:59,049 --> 00:20:59,925
Yes.

400
00:21:05,014 --> 00:21:07,516
I'll kill him.
I'll kill him no matter what.

401
00:21:07,975 --> 00:21:10,186
I've come this far,
I won't let them stop me.

402
00:21:10,269 --> 00:21:13,230
I'm not giving up
until I have everything.

403
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,942
[laughs maniacally]

404
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:33,709
TO BE CONTINUED

405
00:21:38,631 --> 00:21:40,382
[theme music plays]
